formula.text: COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN ACTIVATION_COUNT("_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>") >= 2 THEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."_CASE_KEY" ELSE NULL END)

COUNT(DISTINCT 
      CASE WHEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" IN (<%=Repeated%>)
      AND ACTIVATION_COUNT("_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>") >= 2 
      THEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."_CASE_KEY" ELSE NULL END
)
KPI("Repeated Activity Rate", VARIABLE(<%= process %>), VARIABLE(<%= language %>), VARIABLE(<%= Repeated %>), VARIABLE(<%= CASE_TABLE %>))

components.title: # Repetitions

axis0.name: #{activity}
axis0.text: CASE WHEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>"  IN (<%= Repeated %>) THEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" ELSE NULL END

axis2.name: # <%= CASE_ITEM %>s with Repeated Activities
axis2.text:
COUNT(DISTINCT 
    CASE 
        WHEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>"  IN (<%= Repeated %>) 
        AND ACTIVATION_COUNT("_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>") >= 2 THEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."_CASE_KEY" 
        ELSE NULL 
    END
    )

axis2.name: # Repeated Activities
axis2.text:
--# of repetitions (without the original activity) 
SUM(CASE 
    WHEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>"  IN (<%=Repeated%>) 
    AND ACTIVATION_COUNT("_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>") >= 2 
    THEN ACTIVATION_COUNT("_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>") -1 
    ELSE 0 
END)

variables.title: TIMEFRAME
variables.variableValue:
CASE
WHEN MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT") IN (10,11,12) THEN YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT") || ' - Q1'
WHEN MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT") IN (1,2,3) THEN YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT") || ' - Q2'
WHEN MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT") IN (4,5,6) THEN YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) || ' - Q3'
WHEN MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT") IN (7,8,9) THEN YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT") || ' - Q4'
ELSE NULL
END

variables.title: TIMEFRAME
variables.variableValue:
CASE -- 2 digit Month
WHEN MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT") >= 10
THEN YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT") ||'-' || MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT")
ELSE YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT") ||'-0' || MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT")
END

variables.title: TIMEFRAME
variables.variableValue:
CASE
WHEN CALENDAR_WEEK("EKKO"."AEDAT") >= 10
THEN YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT")
--- ADD one Year if we are already in CW 1 at the end of December
+ CASE WHEN MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT") = 12 AND CALENDAR_WEEK("EKKO"."AEDAT") = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
|| '-CW-' ||CALENDAR_WEEK("EKKO"."AEDAT")
ELSE YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT") || '-CW-0' ||CALENDAR_WEEK("EKKO"."AEDAT")
END

variables.title: TIMEFRAME
variables.variableValue:
CASE -- 2 digit Month
WHEN MONTH( "EKKO"."AEDAT" ) >= 10
THEN CASE
WHEN DAY("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) >= 10
THEN YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) ||'-'|| MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) ||'-' || DAY("EKKO"."AEDAT" )
ELSE YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) ||'-'|| MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) ||'-0' || DAY("EKKO"."AEDAT" )
END
ELSE CASE
WHEN DAY("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) >= 10
THEN YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) ||'-0'|| MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) ||'-' || DAY("EKKO"."AEDAT" )
ELSE YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) ||'-0'|| MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) ||'-0' || DAY("EKKO"."AEDAT" )
END
END
